title: testing against datalad-neuroimaging started to fail

labels.name: fix-implemented
labels.description: A fix is available, but has not been merged or released, yet.

body:
either due to datalad-neuroimaging release or some changes here (happens for PRs against 0.11.x) and I failed so far to reproduce locally (python2)
